nodes.text: Delta Six was the callsign of a TIE/sf space superiority fighter that was stolen by Iden Versio and her daughter Zay Versio during a battle on the planet Vardos concurrent to the Hosnian Cataclysm in 34 ABY. Iden and Zay were accompanied by Shriv Suurgav of the Resistance on another starfighter, and used them to board the Retribution.
